{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>有$n$个函数，分别为$F\\_1,F\\_2,...,F\\_n$。定义$F\\_i(x)=A\\_ix^2+B\\_ix+C\\_i(x∈N\\*)$。给定这些$A\\_i、B\\_i$和$C\\_i$，请求出所有函数的所有函数值中最小的$m$个（如有重复的要输出多个）。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"最小函数值 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>将这$n$个函数所有可以生成的函数值排序后的前$m$个元素。这$m$个数应该输出到一行，用空格隔开。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行输入两个正整数$n$和$m$。<p><p>以下$n$行每行三个正整数，其中第$i$行的三个数分别位$A\\_i$、$B\\_i$和$C\\_i$。输入数据保证$A\\_i≤10，B\\_i≤100，C\\_i≤10000$。<p>","examples":"<input>3 10\n4 5 3\n3 4 5\n1 7 1\n</input><output>9 12 12 19 25 29 31 44 45 54\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"【数据规模】\n$n,m≤10000$。\n","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1370","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}